<l>payaṉṟūkkār ceyta vutavi nayaṉṟūkki</l>
<l>ṉaṉmai kaṭaliṟ peritu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If one weigh the goodness of the help those do who do not weigh results,</l>
<l>it is an excellence far greater than the sea.</l>
